column4: Tech group sides with Apple in Qualcomm's iPhone ban dispute
column5: A group representing major technology companies has aligned itself against Qualcomm Inc in its legal dispute with Apple Inc by calling on regulators to reject Qualcomm's bid to ban the import of iPhones.

column4: Arista loses bid to lift import ban in Cisco battle
column5: The U.S. government on Thursday dealt Arista Networks Inc a loss in its technology dispute with Cisco Systems Inc and refused to set aside an order blocking importation of some of Arista's network switches.
